name: KStew Vanity Fair Clutch
description:
A unique, one-of-a-kind & handmade clutch made from the pages of Vanity Fair magazine. Adorned with a shimmery white button. Velcro closure. Measures 7 x 6 inches.

This clutch was made prior to the disastrous Robsten breakup!

Utilize the contact button on the side bar for additional photos of this fabulous clutch!

name: Zebra Clutch
description:
This unique handmade clutch is laminate-lined with brown zebra cloth & is adorned with a florescent green button. Uses Velcro tabs for closure. Measures 12x9.5 inches.

Durable enough to house an iPad, or to discretely store feminine products.
